==English==
===Verb form===
'''sawing'''

#Present partiple of [[saw]] (process of cutting with a serrated blade).
#:''We spent all day '''sawing''' wood, it would have gone faster if the saw had been sharper.''
#Moving back and forth (resembling the motion of a saw blade being used).
#:''The actor kept '''sawing''' the air with his hands, they kept moving back and forth and it looked like sooner or later the leading lady would get a black eye.''